trainee_entry_requirements.page_content: Can communicate both orally and in writing; Can perform mensuration and calculation; and any of the three: Holder of AE NC II, or Holder of NC on Crop Production, Animal Production, Aquaculture, and Food Processing; With two (2) year experience for the last five (5) years in any of the above-mentioned areas (Agroenterprise, Crop Production, Animal Production, Aquaculture, and Food Processing); Graduate of Agriculture-related courses in any of the above-mentioned areas (Agroenterprise, Crop Production, Animal Production, Aquaculture, and Food Processing)
